title: God's Ear
desc:
God's Ear by Jenny Schwartz 
 Directed by Jenna Rossman 
 Ted and Mel lost their son. Lanie lost her brother. 
 They will sing about it. They will rhyme about it. They will dream about it. They will avoid about it. 
 And everything else will move in a circle of snow around them. 
 CAST 
 Madison Pollack as Mel 
 Nick Wheelehon as Ted 
 Helena Anderson as Lanie 
 Tori Khalil as Tooth Fairy 
 JB Douglas as Flight Attendant and GI Joe 
 Paolo Ragusa as Guy 
 Sveta Pyntikova as Lenora 
 
 
 CREATIVE 
 Set design by Patrick Korkuch 
 Lighting design by Elizabeth Stewart 
 Costume Design by Ryan Wilbat 
 Assistant costume design by Savannah Grinell 
 Sound design by Nathan Rubio? 
 Stage managed by Phil Kenner?
